Document: VisualShaderNodeGroupBase
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodegroupbase.rst
Summary: Base class for all visual shader node groups.

Inherits: VisualShaderNode < Resource

This is the base class for all visual shader node groups. It provides basic functionality for managing nodes within a group, such as adding, removing, and querying them. It also handles the serialization and deserialization of the group's contents.

Key Rule: Node groups are used to organize and encapsulate complex shader logic into reusable components. They allow for a more modular and maintainable visual shader graph.
---CHUNK---
